  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME THE WYVERN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take flight as a prehistoric wyvern and battle for dominance in a fast-paced aerial arena shooter built around skill, movement, and mastery. Breathe fire, launch explosive firebolts, dodge and roll through the air, and unleash powerful special attacks as you outmaneuver opponents and control the skies. Every match is a chance to refine your skills and become a more dangerous threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOCAL FIRST, NETWORKED SECOND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable forever, with or without a network. Fight against adjustable difficulty CPUs on all available game modes and maps. Offline play earns the same rewards and progression as multiplayer, making it perfect for players who want a competitive experience without needing fast internet speeds or groups of friends. Practice new strategies, try different abilities, and sharpen your gameplay, entirely at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=434 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMMUNITY MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyfear offers a server browser for multiplayer battles, plus a dedicated LAN network mode for parties or competitive tournaments. Battle settings in any setup can be fully customized to make playing with your friends different every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill-based aerial arena combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline single-player battles against CPU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable abilities and loadouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extensive character and profile customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple maps, modes, and playstyles to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAN party and online multiplayer support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards (includes single player progress)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No microtransactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No online-only content</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mouse & keyboard input is highly recommended.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>100% human-made. This production does not use any AI-generated assets or code.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME THE WYVERN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take flight as a prehistoric wyvern and battle for dominance in a fast-paced aerial arena shooter built around skill, movement, and mastery. Breathe fire, launch explosive firebolts, dodge and roll through the air, and unleash powerful special attacks as you outmaneuver opponents and control the skies. Every match is a chance to refine your skills and become a more dangerous threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/186051fe92fbaf47adb142c3a5ab7ba3.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOCAL FIRST, NETWORKED SECOND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable forever, with or without a network. Fight against adjustable difficulty CPUs on all available game modes and maps. Offline play earns the same rewards and progression as multiplayer, making it perfect for players who want a competitive experience without needing fast internet speeds or groups of friends. Practice new strategies, try different abilities, and sharpen your gameplay, entirely at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=434 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/e99c7af7c3752a439351e51f3675df5f.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMMUNITY MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skyfear offers a server browser for multiplayer battles, plus a dedicated LAN network mode for parties or competitive tournaments. Battle settings in any setup can be fully customized to make playing with your friends different every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.poster.avif?t=1773672145\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.webm?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814330/extras/35334b82a6b3bd5caf53d9d869ed49df.mp4?t=1773672145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill-based aerial arena combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline single-player battles against CPU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable abilities and loadouts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extensive character and profile customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple maps, modes, and playstyles to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LAN party and online multiplayer support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards (includes single player progress)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No microtransactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No online-only content</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Mouse & keyboard input is highly recommended.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>100% human-made. This production does not use any AI-generated assets or code.</i></p>",
